parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Coolant Level Sensor Retainer Clip Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the coolant level sensor retainer clips can cause the sensor to become dislodged, leading to coolant leaks, engine overheating, and potential engine damage.
symptoms: Coolant warning light flashes
puddles of antifreeze under the vehicle
coolant level sensor not retained properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the oxygen sensor can cause loud muffler noise, engine trouble lights to come on, and potentially affect the ABS system.
symptoms: Loud muffler noise
engine trouble light comes on
oxygen sensor comes out of the exhaust train.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine mount bolts can cause loss of steering control, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Engine mount bolts break off while driving
loss of steering control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine overheating can cause engine damage, shutdowns, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Engine continually overheating
engine shutting down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden loss of power can cause accidents, especially if it occurs at high speeds.
symptoms: Vehicle loses total power without warning
no indication of power loss before it happens.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioner cooling system can cause discomfort and distraction while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The air conditioner cooling temperature is lower than normal
the air conditioner stops cooling
and the condenser unit may need to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, especially when the vehicle continues to move forward despite attempts to brake.
symptoms: The brakes fail to engage
the vehicle continues to move forward
the ABS light comes on
and the brake rotors may need to be replaced frequently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause the vehicle to skid or lose control, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The ABS light comes on
the wheels lock up
and the vehicle skids or loses control.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Power Door Lock and Power Window Problems
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power door lock and power window systems can cause inconvenience and distraction while driving.
symptoms: The power door locks and power windows malfunction
and the window motors may need to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power window system can cause inconvenience and distraction while driving, potentially leading to accidents due to obstructed visibility.
symptoms: Power windows would not open or close
left front window would not open or close.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A noisy heater blower motor can be a distraction while driving and may indicate a more serious underlying issue with the heating system.
symptoms: Heater blower motor becomes noisy after having the heater on for a while.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sun glazing on the windshield can cause poor visibility while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Poor visibility when driving due to sun glazing on the windshield.
